#   {id: 3, name: "Web App Developer Basic", tagline: "Give yourself the opportunity to earn a great income as a web application developer. Work for a tech startup, or create your own.", description: "<p class=\"lead\"><strong>Do you want to learn web application development fast?</strong> Trying to teach yourself online could take you up to twelve months. The Coder Factory teaches you all the shortcuts in just 8 weeks.</p>\r\n<p>By choosing the Web App Developer programme, you will have fun learning to build web applications in supportive, face to face workshops. The teachers care about your success and you will make new friends, meeting other people who have similar interests and ambitions to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In each workshop you will pick up valuable skills through practical, hands on coding exercises and learn powerful knowledge with important background computer science theory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We get a kick out of seeing the look on our students' faces when they realise they can build anything they want with their new found coding skills. Even if they already had an idea about what they wanted to build, they now have a whole heap more.</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">In summary:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Face to face classes help you learn fast</li>\r\n<li>Supportive teachers care about your success</li>\r\n<li>Small class sizes - no more than 12, usually less than 10</li>\r\n<li>Network and make new friends</li>\r\n<li>Learn valuable skills and important knowledge</li>\r\n<li>Find out what is possible with web application development - give yourself a whole new world of possibilities</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Learn a wide range of valuable skills and powerful knowledge</p>\r\n<dl>\r\n<dt>Application design</dt><dd>learn the steps to design an application that people want to use</dd>\r\n<dt>Database design</dt><dd>knowing how databases work helps you build powerful applications</dd>\r\n<dt>Software design patterns</dt><dd>understand how modern programming platforms help you create applications efficiently</dd>\r\n<dt>User interface design</dt><dd>find out about the tools and frameworks that make designing web interfaces easy and fast</dd>\r\n<dt>Software development tools</dt><dd>learn to use all the great open source tools available to developers today</dd>\r\n<dt>Advanced web application functionality</dt><dd>after this programme, you could build your own Facebook if you want!</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<hr>\r\n<p class=\"lead\">Is this programme for you?</p>\r\n<ul class=\"fa-ul\">\r\n<li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></i>Do you have some basic web design and programming experience?</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></i>Have you tried to teach yourself online but given up?</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></i>Do you want to take advantage of the technology revolution that is happening now?</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></i>Have you realised that being able to code will supercharge your career?</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></i>Do you have an app idea that you know solves a problem for people?</li>\r\n<li><i class=\"fa-li fa fa-arrow-circle-right\"></i>Do you want to work in a tech startup?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If you answered yes to any of these, this programme is for you.</p>", created_at: "2014-05-22 08:30:10", updated_at: "2014-06-02 14:52:51", slug: "web-application-developer-programme", image: "city3.jpg", price: 2150, icon: "graduation-cap"}
